 MBOMBELA – An anonymous tip-off led to the arrest of a man in his early 30s in Riverside Industrial this afternoon. According to a trusted source, he had on him schedule four and five substances, the possession of which is deemed illegal.  After the police obtained a warrant, the premises at which the suspect is employed was searched. A large quantity of substances was allegedly seized. The suspect cannot yet be identified as he has not yet appeared in court. He is set to appear tomorrow morning. The substance allegedly found in his possession is being advertised on Instagram to assist in getting “jacked for summer”.          